Package: async
Version: 0.4.0
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.2),
  listenv,
  future
Imports:
  BatchJobs (>= 1.6.0),
  globals,
  parallel,
  R.methodsS3,
  R.oo,
  R.utils
Title: Asynchronous Evaluation
Authors@R: c(person("Henrik", "Bengtsson", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                                          email = "henrikb@braju.com"))
Description: Easy asynchronous evaluation of R expressions based on the Future API defined by the 'future' package and automatically handling of global variables the with help of the 'globals' package.
License: Private for now [will become LGPL (>= 2.1) when published]
LazyLoad: TRUE
